                          <h1 class="title">Accommodation</h1>
                                
        
        <div id="content-area">
          <div id="node-432" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  

  <div class="content">
    <p>You can find some information about sleeping in Gothenburg at <a href="http://wikitravel.org/en/G%C3%B6teborg#Sleep">Wikitravel Göteborg: Sleeping</a> and on <a href="http://www.vastsverige.com/en/West-Sweden/Accomodation/Accomodation/?df=&amp;dt=&amp;a=53&amp;per=&amp;rad=1">Västsverige (West Sweden)</a>.</p>
<p>When looking for accommodation, it's good to select something which is close to a tram line, or even better: bus number 16, which will take you directly to the FSCONS venue.</p>
<h2>Hotels</h2>
<p>The following hotels are recommended for FSCONS participants. They are both reasonably located for travels to and from the FSCONS venue.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.hotel11.se/">Quality Hotel 11</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.accorhotels.com/gb/hotel-2896-ibis-goteborg-city/index.shtml">Ibis Göteborg City Hotel</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Hostels</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.hostel-gothenburg.com/">Hostelling International Stigbergsliden</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sgsveckobostader.se/">SGS Veckobostäder</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.slottsskogenvh.se/">Slottsskogens Youth Hostel</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.goteborgsvandrarhem.se/">Göteborgs Vandrarhem</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.vandrarhem.com/content">Kvibergs Hostel</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.grethes.com/eg.htm">Grethe's Hostel</a></li>
</ul>
  </div>

